snippet.title: Donkey Kong vs. K. Rool Challenge launch trailer (A new Donkey Kong Land Fan game 2021)
snippet.description:
Donkey Kong Land VS. K. Rool, also know as Donkey Kong vs. K. Rool Challenge, is another fan game by Nimaginendo Games produced by Vinícius Lemos to celebrate Donkey Kong's 40th Anniversary.

This, reimagines K. Rool's Kingdom level from Donkey Kong Land, in 16-bits pre-rendered DKC SNES style. The story is different from the original game! This time K. Rool captured Diddy Kong. He also wants to destroy DK Island with TNTs. Are you ready to rematch this battle in a new style?

Vini: I started producing this fan game in July, day 11. And finished the work in the day 21. So in day 22 I fixed some really bad bugs and re-released the fan game on the Kiddy Kong's Show Time facebook page. Also a very more easy battle was added.  Before was only 1 DK Barrel and now had various during the K. Rool battle. The last update was in the day 24, fixed K. Rool's mask when he is walking.

Trailer made by Vini and Jacob

Vinicius - DKC style sound effects + text + fan game and videos from the gameplay of the fan game + fan game logos

Jacob - Added effects + musics from start + K. Rool and new DK voice with pitch changes, added fast speed to the fan game gameplay videos.

Download:
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1QagHlKba1dXopKq3byl_VcEJZi5X6qEH/view?usp=sharing

Characters and stuffs are (C) of Nintendo 1995 - 2021
